Author: GRAHAM
Vol / Page: 191
Edition:
Quote: NEW ZEALAND SAND-FLOUNDER (PATIKI) <i>Rhombosolea plebeia</i> (Richardson)... In and around Nelson the Sand-flounder is known as Plaice. It is not unlike this fish in shape, but the English Plaice is of a deep brown colour with orange-red spots on the upper surface.
